Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.27,0:00:06.02,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please can you keep my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:23.50,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror, shining so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:29.34,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how do I look in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.76,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The future, beckoning me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:38.64,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen from now, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:49.90,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because what we see is not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:52.74,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing myself but that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.32,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now try not to waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:01:00.28,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be true to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.04,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But even I have a secret or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:10.59,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That I want to keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:16.34,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my secret makes my heart aches slightly.
