Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is last month's financial report done?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, confirm the location for the next major cleanup-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Takumi here already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you! How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's relaxing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the library if you want to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council room is not a place for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often see him hanging around her recently... Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you mean Shintani? I heard he was her childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She took care of him when they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I saw dogs glaring at each other just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Pets aren't allowed in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, she's an amazing person!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, do you still have any bread crusts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread crusts taste surprisingly good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys finally realised how great bread crusts truly are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you to abstain from eating in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan, do you want some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about {\i1}that{\i0}, have you told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the part time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Part time job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Misaki-chan is Misa-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you're working part time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What 'bout the part time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he started working at a petrol station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm not gonna tell anyone about your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hush-hush over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, I need to leave for my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, give us the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's things between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys didn't have much chance to converse properly at outdoor education.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it seemed like you guys got closer after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Did something happen between you and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened! He's just my childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot to call him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey grandpa! Hinata here-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?! You didn't even call us, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be that angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny's worried sick, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing fine here! You don't need to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you manage to find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I found her almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the same school, even the same class, as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... must be fate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An anime-cosplay event?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The producers gave us permission to do it after seeing our pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you! You're just perfect for Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Maids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't watched it yet? It's airing on Sunday mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else that can play Mimosa but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you these DVDs, so try to get into the role of your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the 4th season already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's about 40 volumes in this season alone.{that's one fucking long season indeed e: yeah, seriously, wtf.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to watch them all. Just watch episode 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And episode 12 and 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this volume's pretty popular as well, so I recommend this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what happened after Hinata found out about your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can answer that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Usui become jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Usui, he's not here today. I didn't see him in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a perverted alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani! You can leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to tell me what shift you want next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry but... I might need to attend supplementary classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're having problems with your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a shoulder massage, so shall I tutor you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't really help much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need a ride back? I have an extra helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I need to make a stop today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This persimmon looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Be good and don't roll away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna dance in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Master's been cursed with black magic and made to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mop Missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids shows nowadays are rather... amazing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mop missiles, huh... There's also rag bombs... {rag as in rag clothes}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mom's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there's a man I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he'll be our new father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten so big! You were so tiny back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hamburger-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for that, Cheese-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Mega Cheese Hamburger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a part from an anime we watched together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do. You don't look tasty at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were much bigger and juicier last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! What should I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose to Tsukimi Burger-kun like this, right, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Misaki-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked up some persimmons I dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met by pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't this happen before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten a lot handsomer, Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I manlier, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You've grown sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that habit of eating persimmons you've picked up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't know it was you who dropped them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you doing near my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-kun, don't tell me that you still like Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuna! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-kun's still as easy to read as he was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I was shy and kept a low profile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one should have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You kept staring at Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you knew about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for our house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't stalk people, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it. I was looking for the cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry tree? You mean the one you fell from that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You remembered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such a troublemaker, You-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go climbing trees again, and make sure to follow me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Misaki-chan.  I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you for life, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right! That part happened in the hospital, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember it that well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to follow you for life, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, that's not what I meant by {\i1}follow me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no matter where it happened, the promise was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This drink tastes rather nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that cherry tree is still there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we'll spend our time here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to today's event!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done my research since Ikkun told us about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first time watching early morning shoujo anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to be melted away by today's Latte Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Master's been cursed with black magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Misa... No, Rose shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kariron Popuron Instant Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time and enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a perfect "Magical Maids" cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The similarity to the original is just amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only watched it once, but I liked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the two main characters. It's just as you predicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't expect Misa-chan to do this much for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was gonna ignore us again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine by me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That error you made when calling her name is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make today's event a complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki, I'm just perfect for Mimosa's character, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You're a boy in middle school, Aoi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go out to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I'm this suitable for the role?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra order, a Witch Parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No-nam-cha-ruru-tte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mam-pu-kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the diet spell? Though I answered you instinctively...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even remembered the core spells that are never really used?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even know anything about this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched all of the DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a lot of time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all of last night finishing them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even pulled an all-nighter for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's coming today as a customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was already a part of the staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do? Are you gonna do the magic girl routine in front of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Melt away with Latte Magic today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems different today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, he would have replied smugly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he really is bothered by Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but it's time for Mimosa to-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, miladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was today's special, the Magical Miracle Parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed it. It was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls in the kitchen wanted to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a pointed spoon when putting the {\i1}quenelles{\i0} on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll get better with some practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quene-{\i0} Pointed spoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this parfait, the frills around the rose decoration was nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I think the sponge cake inside should be a little firmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a lot of opinions you have there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I write them down on a memo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, just who are you, Usui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just another ordinary guy, that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain someone has been calling me this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so just think of me as another perverted alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan! I've come to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, you knew about Misa-chan working here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are here to see her as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Misaki-chan, but Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the law here in Maid Latte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's event is not an all-you-can-eat. Are you fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting interesting, isn't it? It's all that dimwit's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Time to use the patch-up spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukinpa, Wakunpa, Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not strong enough! They need some of Mimosa's Boys Love Spell- {CAST IT YOU BITCH! e: LOL THE FANFICTION. I CAN SEE IT ALREADY.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to go out, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Magical Russian Roulette!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the special event today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one of these contains a magical juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who drinks it has to put on a straight face, and I have to guess who drank it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you beat me, you can choose either a specially-made coaster, or a commemoration photo-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The photo, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cast a spell right now. Don't hold back on me, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what kind of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spell that renders you incapable of lying~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorinpa Dorunpa! Now you can't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This juice is... no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who drank the magical juice is Master Kurotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, give me some water...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe journey, masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pull back for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurotatsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks interesting! I wanna try it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What spell would you like, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about... a spell to beat my rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to beat me by magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a point! You gotta win it by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the love spell is a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it succeeds, there will be a price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I don't like scary stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shivering just from listening to the scary consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a spell that I'd like you to cast on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Seeking spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that cherry tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, cast on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cast it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Derunpa Deronpa! You'll find it soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi seems moody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pouting about not being to get out to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped you with the outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even helped you with the acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked so cute as Mimosa, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just butted in forcefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show off on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why are you alone here on a holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go make some friends to play with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be lectured by you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is not a playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It doesn't matter to you whether I have friends or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one who's alone! Usui's alone all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he doesn't have any friends at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, right, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, his friends? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yukimura his friend? No, more like a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kanou his friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, isn't that obvious enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It doesn't feel like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so at first, but I'm not sure he thinks we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thought"? You used past tense just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me change my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he to me now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's suspicious to hang out around here at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be taken as a pervert! What are you thinking, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny to see a magical girl taking out the trash. Isn't there a spell for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try casting another spell, like just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face's really red, Ayuzawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's rather cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel cold? Wear a coat if you're gonna be out at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure like to worry about others, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I planned to walk home just like this, but I felt like seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look that solitary to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you heard what we said just now-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of that, I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that last question- I want to know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what am I to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is what you do when you can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're not honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's embarrassing, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what my feelings are, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you sexual harassing alien! If someone sees us like this-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorinpa, Dorunpa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even a magical girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you use spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, Misaki-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It has nothing to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that it's still here. It's grown quite a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}The event in Maid Latte this time was a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}I was even knocked out by the magical juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}This is truly a fearsome heart-shocking event! Heart Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}I don't know what you guys are saying, but never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Misaki Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Why is everyone calling for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to circle around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a UxMishi live performance at the Cultural Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you learnt your lesson yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,687)}I just wanted to call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,687)}Just what do you want me to do?!
